                <h1>Early voting has started. Here&#039;s how to do it on campus</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/873e840f-e56e-4ee2-b8b2-350d968c4202.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

